OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FThe husband of a Labour MP and two
OL,8,Fother men have been released on bail
OL,9,Fafter being arrested on suspicion of
OL,10,Fspying for China.
OL,12,FDavid Taylor, the wife of Scottish
OL,13,FLabour MP Joani Reid, is accused of
OL,14,Fassisting a foreign intelligence
OL,15,Fservice.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
