OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FThe Metropolitan Police said that
OL,8,FTaylor, 39, and two other men, aged 43
OL,9,Fand 68, were arrested by counter-
OL,10,Fterrorism officers at addresses in
OL,11,FLondon and Wales on Wednesday and have
OL,12,Fbeen released on bail until May.
OL,14,FFollowing Taylor's arrest, his wife Ms
OL,15,FReid said she had "never seen anything
OL,16,Fto make me suspect my husband has
OL,17,Fbroken any law".
OL,19,FMs Reid sits on the Home Affairs
OL,20,FSelect Committee and is MP for East
OL,21,FKilbride and Strathaven,
OL,26,@wD@SOUyD@OO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FThe three men were taken into custody
OL,8,Ffor questioning by police before being
OL,9,Freleased on bail.
OL,11,FThe policing operation came as
OL,12,Fsecurity minister Dan Jarvis told MPs
OL,13,FChinese officials in the UK and
OL,14,FBeijing had been given a dressing
OL,15,Fdown, and that the investigation
OL,16,Frelates to "foreign interference
OL,17,Ftargeting UK democracy".
OL,26,@xD@LOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FMet officers were seen at a property
OL,8,Flinked to one of the men in South
OL,9,FWales on Wednesday ` with a car
OL,10,Foutside the address being searched and
OL,11,Fphotographed.
OL,13,FTaylor is listed as a "lobbyist" on Ms
OL,14,FReid's registered interests.
OL,16,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,17,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,18,Fpreviously said the force does not
OL,19,Fbelieve there to be "any imminent or
OL,20,Fdirect threat" related to the arrests.
OL,26,@uD@WOUuD@`O]{D@UOU|D@NO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FTaylor was arrested in London, the 43-
OL,8,Fyear-old man was arrested in Pontyclun
OL,9,Fin South Wales, and the 68-year-old
OL,10,Fsuspect was arrested in the county of
OL,11,FPowys in mid-Wales ` with all three
OL,12,Fbeing detained under the Police and
OL,13,FCriminal Evidence Act.
OL,15,FOther properties in London, East
OL,16,FKilbride in Scotland, and Cardiff have
OL,17,Falso been searched, the Met said.
OL,19,FIn her statement after the arrests, Ms
OL,20,FReid said:
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,F"I have never been to China. I have
OL,8,Fnever spoken on China or China-related
OL,9,Fmatters in the Commons.
OL,11,F"I have never asked a question on
OL,12,FChina-related matters.
OL,14,F"As far as I am aware, I have never
OL,15,Fmet any Chinese businesses whilst I
OL,16,Fhave been an MP, any Chinese diplomats
OL,17,For government employees, nor raised
OL,18,Fany concern with ministers or anyone
OL,19,Felse on behalf of, even
OL,20,Fcoincidentally, Chinese interests."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU|D@cO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/7
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1772712216
OL,3,CThree men released on bail after being
OL,4,Carrested on suspicion of spying for
OL,5,CChina
OL,7,FShe added: "I am not any sort of
OL,8,Fadmirer or apologist for the Chinese
OL,9,FCommunist Party's dictatorship.
OL,11,F"I have never seen anything to make me
OL,12,Fsuspect my husband has broken any law."
OL,26,@oD@LOUsD@AOUtD@gO]
